224
00:29:07,286 --> 00:29:08,763
<i>Usai Perang Dingin...</i>

225
00:29:09,719 --> 00:29:12,161
<i>...Umbrella Corporation
memperluasnya...</i>

226
00:29:12,206 --> 00:29:14,858
